			<div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="350" height="290" src="http://marcusgrahamproject.org/mg-rebuild/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Evolv305x290.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="evolv305x290" srcset="http://marcusgrahamproject.org/mg-rebuild/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Evolv305x290.jpg 350w, http://marcusgrahamproject.org/mg-rebuild/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Evolv305x290-300x249.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" /></div>
